text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_DoubleBattleAdvice1 {
	"Sure, there are several places where
	you can enter DOUBLE BATTLES.

	But the DOUBLE BATTLE ROOMS of
	the BATTLE TOWER are, like, basic!

	They're where you should learn about
	how DOUBLE BATTLES are played here
	in the BATTLE FRONTIER."
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_DoubleBattleAdvice2 {
	"Watch yourself in the battles here.

	I hear there are TRAINERS that have
	strategies they developed just for
	DOUBLE BATTLES."
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_DoubleBattleAdvice3 {
	"Once you're confident and comfortable
	with DOUBLE BATTLES here, you should
	think about challenging other places
	offering DOUBLE BATTLES."
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_MultiBattleAdvice {
	"All sorts of TRAINERS gather in
	the BATTLE SALON.

	Just think--you may run into your
	friends or followers!
	You should look carefully!"
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_LinkMultiBattleAdvice {
	"If you're with a friend, head for the
	LINK MULTI BATTLE ROOM.

	If you play with a strong friend,
	you can expect to see tough foes!"
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_NewsGatheringPower {
	"What amazing news-gathering power!
	My mentor's like none other!"
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_AmazingPowersOfObservation {
	"What amazing powers of observation!
	My mentor's like none other!"
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_AmazingPowerOfPersuasion {
	"What amazing power of persuasion!
	My mentor's like none other!"
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge2_Text_ThisPlaceIsScaringMe {
	"…What is this place?
	It's scaring me…"
}

